Implemented the minimal source fix.

Changed:
- `gson/src/main/java/com/google/gson/Gson.java`
  - `FutureTypeAdapter` now exposes its resolved serialization delegate through an internal interface.
- `gson/src/main/java/com/google/gson/internal/bind/TypeAdapterRuntimeTypeWrapper.java`
  - Runtime adapter selection now unwraps delegating adapters before deciding whether an adapter is reflective.
- Added:
  - `gson/src/main/java/com/google/gson/internal/bind/SerializationDelegatingTypeAdapter.java`

Validation:
- Manually compiled sources with `javac --release 8` and verified the provided cyclic `Base` / `Sub` example now outputs:
  - `{"f":{"i":2}}`

No test files were modified.
